University |religion = Roman Catholicism |website = [http://collins.senate.gov/
Government website] }} 'Susan Margaret Collins' (born December 7, 1952) is the
senior United States Senator from Maine and a member of the Republican Party.
First elected to the Senate in 1996, she is the ranking member of the Senate
Special Committee on Aging.
